## Verifying this release

This release is signed end-to-end with [Sigstore](https://www.sigstore.dev/) keyless signing.

### Verify the Git tag

The `${TAG_NAME}` tag is signed with [gitsign](https://github.com/sigstore/gitsign):

```sh
gitsign verify-tag \
  --certificate-identity="${CERTIFICATE_IDENTITY}" \
  --certificate-oidc-issuer="https://token.actions.githubusercontent.com" \
  ${TAG_NAME}
```

### Verify the release images

Release artifacts are published as signed container images and are not attached
to this GitHub release. To verify the frontend image for this release with
[cosign](https://github.com/sigstore/cosign):

```sh
cosign verify ghcr.io/${IMAGE_REPO}/frontend:${TAG_NAME} \
  --certificate-oidc-issuer="https://token.actions.githubusercontent.com" \
  --certificate-identity="https://github.com/${IMAGE_REPO}/.github/workflows/frontend-image.yml@refs/tags/${TAG_NAME}"
```

See the [image verification guide](https://project-dalec.github.io/dalec/verifying-images)
for worker images and `gh attestation verify` instructions.
